---
title: Golden Chicken & Honey Glaze with Roasted Veggies, Apple Slaw & Garlic-Peppercorn Hollandaise
description: Golden and glowing, that’s how we like our chicken and the combination of our Aussie spice blend and honey coating
doesn’t disappoint. The roasted potato and carrot shine just as bright on the plate, perfect for dipping in a garlic
hollandaise. Dig in and enjoy, we know you will love it!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/onion-chutney-chicken-parmesan-crumb-3b175179.jpg
